June 4, 1962.*

No.-.

In re Shields.

Mr. Justice Frankfurter took no part in the consideration or decision of cases in which orders were this day announced.

Henry R. Shields, Esquire, of New York, New York, having resigned as a member of the Bar of this Court, it is ordered that his name be stricken from the roll of attorneys admitted to practice in this Court.
